headline: Delta Air Lines CEO makes a bold call on airline industry trend
summary: The U.S. airline industry is dominated by four major players: Delta Air Lines, American Airlines, United Airlines, and Southwest Airlines. Competition is fierce, and flyers' demands and expectations are constantly growing. Political and geopolitical turbulence make smooth flying more ...
